data.description:
BACK ON MARKET! REDUCED! 4 bed 3 bath, single story home w designated study, separate family or flex room, 3 car garage, pool, patio with pergola, and tall ceilings! The backyard is fully fenced, private, and has recently had artificial turf added. Kitchen opens to the large family room, and dry bar area.  Cooktop CAN be gas or electric. Gas connection already in place. The 3 car garage features epoxy flooring.  
Lantana is known for its exceptional amenities, including parks, walking trails, golf courses, and community pools. It's a family-friendly neighborhood with a strong sense of community and a convenient location for schools, shopping, and dining.
This single-story gem in Lantana offers a functional and comfortable lifestyle, making it the perfect place to call home. Whether you're enjoying family time in the spacious living areas, working from your home office, or lounging by the pool, this property has everything you need to live your best life in style.
